141
00:25:37,075 --> 00:25:38,653
What are they doing?

142
00:25:38,744 --> 00:25:42,576
Help! Molly, tell them to stop!

143
00:25:50,341 --> 00:25:55,550
Everyone wants to take money from me: The hospital, the fire department...

144
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:58,345
And now you fill my ears with your opera.

145
00:25:58,435 --> 00:26:01,306
This would express our best feelings.

146
00:26:02,439 --> 00:26:05,394
Our best wishes!

147
00:26:05,486 --> 00:26:07,312
We can't have everything.

148
00:26:08,822 --> 00:26:10,731
Take note of this.

149
00:26:11,451 --> 00:26:13,775
Come closer.

150
00:26:13,869 --> 00:26:16,409
Come a little closer.

151
00:26:20,461 --> 00:26:22,750
A small demonstration.

152
00:26:25,926 --> 00:26:29,261
