153
00:26:33,894 --> 00:26:37,180
Did you see how quickly the money disappears?

154
00:26:37,274 --> 00:26:39,516
You must have experienced this.

155
00:26:39,609 --> 00:26:42,695
Of course, a lot of money had to be invested in the railroad.

156
00:26:44,115 --> 00:26:47,532
How exciting it must have been to be ruined!

157
00:26:47,619 --> 00:26:49,907
Let's return to our friends.

158
00:26:49,997 --> 00:26:54,707
Yes, the opportunity to see friends and rivals in the same place...

159
00:26:54,752 --> 00:26:56,829
